{"tid":1488361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[文宣]居港加拿大人可參予聯邦大選","createTime":"2019-08-19T15:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T02:49:45.000Z","uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9baac3f70c26b1a345f294e060ab7f7827b1aa","tid":1488361,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"加拿大在港公民自2019年初可以以郵寄方法參予聯邦大選<br />\n詳情可以參考劉先生解說<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />﹕<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bz81Rmdp3GQ?t=1922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fbz81Rmdp3GQ%3Ft%3D1922&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=de15c78f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bz81Rmdp3GQ?t=1922</a><br />\n時間緊迫，希望各居港加拿大人可以登記，投下你神聖一票<br />\n聯邦大選官網:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elections.ca\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.ca&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=632ec72e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.ca</a><br />\n文宣巴打請幫忙廣傳<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">遍地開花，天佑香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f18869ea0abd20e5df755c25c52911c394ac7a1e","tid":1488361,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:06:34.000Z","msg":"20"},{"pid":"bb7a9bc3a872fc74061c98e7f97ff16c3ebf6a92","tid":1488361,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fbfee8db58a9681fc3d15bd8967f5d4f0d2658f8","tid":1488361,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"19"},{"pid":"e3a675cb16fc6849f74c7c56185